OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1993FThe first edition of Whatever
OL,7,FHappened To...? airs on BBC One.
OL,8,
OL,9,FRadio Times: "Jan Leeming traces the
OL,10,Fstories that hit the headlines - until
OL,11,Fthe news moved on. This week: what
OL,12,Fhappened to the early satellites like
OL,13,FTelstar, the children who survived the
OL,14,FAberfan disaster, peace protestors at
OL,15,FGreenham Common and Britain's first
OL,16,FEurovision."
OL,17,
OL,18,FOther presenters on this daytime
OL,19,Fprogramme: Kenneth Kendall, Richard
OL,20,FWhitmore, Gordon Honeycombe and Angela
OL,21,FRippon.
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
