OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2000FAfter more than eleven years on
OL,7,Fthe channel, Home and Away is shown on
OL,8,FITV for the final time. The programme
OL,9,Fmoved to Channel 5, where its first
OL,10,Fairing was on 16th July 2001.
OL,11,
OL,12,FThe gap of just over a year was due to
OL,13,Fa clause in ITV's contract which
OL,14,Fprevented the programme being broadcast
OL,15,Fin the UK for at least twelve months.
OL,16,
OL,17,CG2002FThe first edition of Ant & Dec's
OL,18,FSaturday Night Takeaway airs on ITV 1.
